\" class=\"wp-image-55820\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/21224600\/creative-small-open-kitchen-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/21224600\/creative-small-open-kitchen-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/21224600\/creative-small-open-kitchen-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/21224600\/creative-small-open-kitchen-design-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/21224600\/creative-small-open-kitchen-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Blend creativity with practicality<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Small Open Concept Kitchen With Island<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have some extra room in the heart of your kitchen, consider adding a small island. Check out this rustic-finished open-layout kitchen featuring an island with a built-in hob unit, essential overhead and base cabinets, and a tall unit with designated spaces for kitchen appliances.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pro Tip:<\/strong> Opt for a tall unit to free up platform space in a compact kitchen.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/21224551\/small-open-kitchen-design-with-island.jpg\" alt=\"Small open kitchen design with an island, which has a rustic look\" class=\"wp-image-55819\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/21224551\/small-open-kitchen-design-with-island.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/21224551\/small-open-kitchen-design-with-island-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/21224551\/small-open-kitchen-design-with-island-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/21224551\/small-open-kitchen-design-with-island-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/21224551\/small-open-kitchen-design-with-island-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A rustic, small, open-concept kitchen with an island<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Spice It Up! Small Open Kitchen, Indian Style<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Infuse your kitchen with a dash of spice! Indian-style small open kitchen designs radiate warmth and vibrant hues, transforming your cooking space into a mini Bollywood spectacle. Feast your eyes on this design featuring lively yellow laminate overhead cabinets, floating shelves, base cabinets, and a countertop with a built-in hob unit. Simplicity meets the richness of Indian kitchen colours in this tastefully minimalistic design.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/21224541\/indian-style-small-open-kitchen-design.jpg\" alt=\"Small open kitchen design in Indian style, which radiates warmth\" class=\"wp-image-55818\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/21224541\/indian-style-small-open-kitchen-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/21224541\/indian-style-small-open-kitchen-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/21224541\/indian-style-small-open-kitchen-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/21224541\/indian-style-small-open-kitchen-design-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/21224541\/indian-style-small-open-kitchen-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Indian-style kitchens are in demand<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Upgrade your old kitchen with a smart space-saving modular kitchen\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/08172005\/upgrade-your-old-kitchen-with-a-smart-space-saving-modular-kitchen.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Small Open Kitchen Ideas With Clever Storage<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Think small, dream big! Uncover brilliant open kitchen ideas for creating cosy nooks that serve multiple purposes. Behold this urban open kitchen in warm wood tones, specially crafted for maximising space in compact homes. Featuring a tall unit with an OTG, oven, and wine rack, a robust 40 Kg tandem drawer for heavy items, and a pull-out breakfast counter doubling as extra cooking space \u2013 it&#8217;s a multitasking marvel. Slide it in when not in use, showcasing smart storage solutions for small spaces.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/21224529\/small-open-kitchen-design-with-storage.jpg\" alt=\"Small open kitchen design with clever storage with an urban look\" class=\"wp-image-55817\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/21224529\/small-open-kitchen-design-with-storage.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/21224529\/small-open-kitchen-design-with-storage-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/21224529\/small-open-kitchen-design-with-storage-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/21224529\/small-open-kitchen-design-with-storage-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/21224529\/small-open-kitchen-design-with-storage-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Small spaces need innovative thinking<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Small Open Kitchen Design in Hall<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ever wondered how to blend an open kitchen into your hall space seamlessly? Check out this cleverly designed kitchen corner, perfect for studio apartments. This space stands out in an open layout and features smart, modular cabinets made for compact, modern living. The combination of brown overhead cabinets, white base cabinets, and a handleless design delivers a seamless look. The tall unit with a built-in microwave adds an urban flair, and tandem drawers offer ample storage. It&#8217;s the perfect blend of style and functionality for small homes.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/21224519\/small-l-shaped-open-kitchen-design.jpg\" alt=\"Small l-shaped open kitchen design which utilises corners perfect for studio apartment\" class=\"wp-image-55816\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/21224519\/small-l-shaped-open-kitchen-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/21224519\/small-l-shaped-open-kitchen-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/21224519\/small-l-shaped-open-kitchen-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/21224519\/small-l-shaped-open-kitchen-design-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/21224519\/small-l-shaped-open-kitchen-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">An L-shaped kitchen that utilises corners<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Conclusion<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>As we navigate the challenges of limited space, these designs unfold a world of possibilities. From the vibrant Indian-style open kitchen designs to multifunctional wonders that offer extra space in small spaces, each design offers an array of benefits.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>So, why wait? <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\">DesignCafe<\/a> offers 51,040 design options, a guaranteed 20% extra space and a warranty of up to 20 years on our products, ensuring you get the home interiors you deserve. Book A FREE Consultation. You can also try customising a kitchen for your home!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">FAQs On Small Open Kitchen Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>What are some layout options for small open kitchens?<\/strong><br>Small open kitchens thrive on clever layouts. Consider options like adding islands, creating multifunctional corners, and utilising vertical space with tall units. The key is to maximise functionality without compromising on style.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>How do you organise an open small Indian kitchen?<\/strong><br>Manage storage with smart solutions like modular cabinets, pull-out drawers, and open shelves. Group similar items, keep essentials within easy reach, and leverage wall space for vertical storage.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>How much does a small open kitchen design cost?<\/strong><br>The cost varies based on factors like designs, materials, appliances, and additional features. However, small open kitchen designs often offer budget-friendly solutions, focusing on practicality and aesthetics without breaking the bank.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>How can I make my small open kitchen feel more spacious?<\/strong><br>Use light colours to create an airy atmosphere, include reflective surfaces, and maximise natural light. Opt for open shelving instead of closed cabinets to maintain an open feel. Declutter regularly to create an illusion of more space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>What are some tips for keeping a small open kitchen clean and tidy?<\/strong><br>Embrace minimalism to avoid overcrowding. Regularly declutter countertops, wipe surfaces after use, and organise storage strategically. Invest in clever storage solutions to maintain order and make cleaning a breeze.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Modular Kitchens At Best Prices<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Speak to our kitchen experts today!<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/span>  -->\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"form-row dc-falg-row\">\n        <!-- <div class=\"form-group col-md-3 guideForm\">\n            <select name=\"your-phone-ext\" id=\"id_select2_example\" class=\"id_select2_example drop-downfield form-dropdown\"\n                onfocus='this.size=5;' onblur='this.size=1;' onchange='this.size=1; this.blur();'\n                data-width=\"100%\" data-minimum-results-for-search=\"Infinity\">\n               \n                <option value=\"+01\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06163948\/01.png\">\n                    +01\n                <\/option>\n                <option value=\"+91\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06164015\/91.png\"\n                    selected>\n                    +91\n                <\/option>\n                <